<div type="letter">

  <pb facs="1416543" n="1r"/>
  <opener>
    <lb/>Vir Amplissime atque Excellentissime,
    <lb/>Patrone ac Fautor plurimum colende</opener>
  
  <p><lb/>Quod si pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sentes seriis Tuis occupationibus molest<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> fuerint,
    <lb/>est cur obnix<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> veniam <add>precer</add>, quam <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> singulari Tua huma<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nitate mihi jam abund<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> perspect<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> facile<del> me impetraturam</del>
    <lb/>spero: Interim non abs re puto si Amplitudini Tu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
    <lb/>significavero, me tandem li<add>b</add>rorum fasci<add>cu</add>lis qui jam <add>ante</add>
    <lb/>bimestr<add>e</add> fere me inscio <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-2661604">Basileam</rs> appulerunt esse poti<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tum. <add>Culpa</add> in eo fuit, quod <abbr>Dn.</abbr> <rs type="person">Reinwaldus</rs> me <add>non</add>
    <lb/>certiorem fecit <add>quando et cui vectur<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> illos trad<unclear>. sint</unclear> sine mora</add> quod uti<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> fieri debebat per cursorem pub<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>licum. Prolixitati huic non minus quam inutili <add>imo</add>
    <lb/>duplici sumtui parci potuisset, si modo <abbr>Ds.</abbr> <rs type="person">Reinwaldus</rs> supelle<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ctilem suam hic <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-2661604">Basile<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> evacuare voluisset, quo ipso
    <lb/>etiam periculum evitasset <add>sibi</add> graviter sane i<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>inens ob
    <lb/>librorum vetitorum convasationem: C<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>terum c<choice><orig><g ref="#ugrav">ù</g></orig><reg>u</reg></choice>m co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>o<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>dior occasio se non obtulerit expensos Tuos 36 grassos<note type="internal">Währungszeichen</note>
    <lb/>un<choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> cum imperiali<note type="internal">Währungszeichen</note> pro <abbr>D.<hi rend="sup">o</hi></abbr> <rs type="person">Reinwaldo</rs>, remisi
    <lb/><abbr>D.</abbr> <rs type="person">Vettinero</rs> vestrati, qui utri<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> vestrum se satisfacturum polli<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>citus.<add> Hoc unicum superest</add> ut gratias <abbr>Excell.</abbr> Tu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> agam, pro pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice><pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>stit<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> oper<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> et officio, quod cert<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> nunquam non demereri adnitar,
    <lb/>faxis mihi nascatur occasio, <add>ut</add> compertum hab<add>eo</add>
    <lb/><add>gratum</add> meum animum <add>meam<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice></add> quantum a tenuitate <add>mea</add> speran<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>d<unclear>a</unclear>m inserviendi promtitudinem. <add>Hisce vale Vir <abbr>Excell.</abbr></add>
    <lb/><add>et favere pergi</add></p>
  
  <closer><lb/>Amplissimi Tui nominis
    <lb/>Cultori studio<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>sissimo
